### Using the UKB RAP 
Locally
Download the DNAnexus toolkit 
Launch a Cloud Workstation 
Inspect it on the UKB-RAP interface (to get Job ID)

# DNA Nexus commands 
dx login 
# Need to set up the SSH-config BEFORE you launch the cloud workstation or it will reject the ssh key
dx ssh job-ID

# Cloud Computing UKB links 
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9I78As5uRfw - youtube video about cloud computing at UKB RAP 

# Downloading BCFTOOLS
git clone --recurse-submodules https://github.com/samtools/htslib.git
git clone https://github.com/samtools/bcftools.git
cd bcftools
make

# Add to the PATH variable 
export PATH="$PATH:~/bcftools"


